<i>noun</i>: 질의 [지릐/지리], 질문 [질문], 의문점 [의문쩜], 의문 [의문], 여부 [여ː부], 물음 [무름], 문항 [문ː항], 문제 [문ː제] <i>verb</i>: 신문하다 [신ː문하다], 문초하다 [문ː초하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>질의 [지릐/지리]</dt><br>
<dd>question; inquiry</dd><br>
<dd>의심이 되거나 모르는 점을 물음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of asking about something one doubts or does not know.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>질문 [질문]</dt><br>
<dd>question</dd><br>
<dd>모르는 것이나 알고 싶은 것을 물음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of asking something one does not know or wants to know.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>의문점 [의문쩜]</dt><br>
<dd>doubtful point; doubt; question</dd><br>
<dd>확실히 알 수 없거나 믿지 못할 만한 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>A part that one cannot understand completely or trust.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>의문 [의문]</dt><br>
<dd>doubt; question</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것에 대해 의심스럽게 생각함. 또는 의심스러운 문제나 사실.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being doubtful of something; a doubtful problem or truth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>여부 [여ː부]</dt><br>
<dd>1. yes or no; whether or not</dd><br>
<dd>그러함과 그러하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>Either yes or no.</dd><br>
<dd>2. room for doubt; question</dd><br>
<dd>틀리거나 의심할 여지.</dd><br>
<dd>The possibility of being wrong or the room for doubt.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>물음 [무름]</dt><br>
<dd>question</dd><br>
<dd>묻는 일. 또는 묻는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of asking, or the words of inquiry.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>문항 [문ː항]</dt><br>
<dd>question</dd><br>
<dd>문제의 항목.</dd><br>
<dd>A query.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>문제 [문ː제]</dt><br>
<dd>1. problem; question</dd><br>
<dd>답을 요구하는 물음.</dd><br>
<dd>A question that demands an answer.</dd><br>
<dd>2. problem; issue</dd><br>
<dd>논쟁이나 논의, 연구 등의 대상이 되는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A matter that is the subject of a debate, discussion, or research.</dd><br>
<dd>3. problem; issue</dd><br>
<dd>난처하거나 해결하기 어려운 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A difficult matter that is awkward or difficult to solve.</dd><br>
<dd>4. trouble</dd><br>
<dd>귀찮은 일이나 말썽.</dd><br>
<dd>A tiresome matter or trouble.</dd><br>
<dd>5. problem; issue</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 사물과 관련되는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A matter that is related to something or an object.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>신문하다 [신ː문하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. question</dd><br>
<dd>이미 알고 있는 일이 사실인지 거짓인지 확인하기 위하여 캐묻다.</dd><br>
<dd>To question inquisitively in order to confirm whether an already known fact is true or false.</dd><br>
<dd>2. interrogate</dd><br>
<dd>정확한 법적 판결을 위해 관계자를 상대로 사건에 대해 캐물으며 조사하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To question inquisitively and investigate people concerned regarding a certain incident for an accurate legal decision.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>문초하다 [문ː초하다]</dt><br>
<dd>question; investigate</dd><br>
<dd>잘못이 있는 사람에게 죄, 잘못 등을 따져 묻거나 심문하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To question or interrogate a guilty person about his/her wrongdoings or crimes.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>